---
title: Herby Ricotta-Topped Farro with Beets, Roasted Squash and Pepitas
description: Packed with veggies and tasty grains, this salad is a perfect complement to light, creamy ricotta. Add a sweet and savoury dressing and honeyed pepitas, and you're set to go with this simple and delicious roast veggie dish!
